<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 01:10:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 和商品期货交易委员会 (CFTC) 定义哪些数字资产是证券</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/sec-cftc-move-to-define-which-digital-assets-are-securities</link><description>美国证券交易委员会周二发布了期待已久的“代币分类法”，这是在明确哪些类型的数字资产被视为证券方面向前迈出的关键一步。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iHHzK3ubKnLg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/sec-cftc-move-to-define-which-digital-assets-are-securities</guid></item><item><title>无许可在去中心化金融中是双向的</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-17/permissionless-works-both-ways-in-decentralized-finance-defi</link><description>DeFi 出了岔子&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iZftIEA6rCys/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-17/permissionless-works-both-ways-in-decentralized-finance-defi</guid></item><item><title>埃里克·特朗普如何成为中国最大的加密货币公司之一的盟友</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-03-17/trump-s-son-and-a-mysterious-chinese-crypto-giant-are-in-business-together</link><description>&lt;p&gt;比特大陆多年来一直受到矿机安全问题的困扰。但这并没有阻止它与第一家庭的一位重要成员开展业务。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFuTRCtHymHY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 20:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2026-03-17/trump-s-son-and-a-mysterious-chinese-crypto-giant-are-in-business-together</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争震撼市场时，比特币作为平静的绿洲令人惊讶</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/bitcoin-surprises-as-oasis-of-calm-while-iran-war-jolts-markets</link><description>自与伊朗的战争爆发以来，加密货币已成为资产类别中的赢家，但数字资产的弹性可能只是时间问题。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iq.WbBpsI2Kk/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 06:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/bitcoin-surprises-as-oasis-of-calm-while-iran-war-jolts-markets</guid></item><item><title>万事达卡以高达 18 亿美元收购稳定币公司 BVNK</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/mastercard-to-buy-stablecoin-startup-bvnk-for-up-to-1-8-billion</link><description>万事达卡公司表示，将以高达 18 亿美元的价格收购稳定币基础设施初创公司 BVNK，四个月前，BVNK 与 Coinbase Global Inc. 就一项约 20 亿美元的交易进行的谈判破裂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ittMqtxNQ0ro/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/mastercard-to-buy-stablecoin-startup-bvnk-for-up-to-1-8-billion</guid></item><item><title>人工智能的货币机器人已经到来，每个人都想处理他们的现金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/the-race-to-bank-ai-agents-in-new-era-of-commerce-is-heating-up</link><description>多年来，稳定币行业一直在等待它的杀手级应用程序——通过为全球范围内的日常​​商业提供动力，该用例将证明数字美元不仅仅是加密货币投机者的工具。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVsyfxBqANMw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/the-race-to-bank-ai-agents-in-new-era-of-commerce-is-heating-up</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者涌入 ETF，比特币触及六周高位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-climbs-in-asia-as-other-markets-remain-tepid</link><description>由于投资者乐观地认为与中东冲突有关的市场动荡可能开始缓解，比特币升至近六周高点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibHEfIi.8Ch8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 05:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-climbs-in-asia-as-other-markets-remain-tepid</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略提高了最新比特币购买中优先股的销量</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/saylor-s-strategy-ramps-up-sales-of-preferred-in-latest-bitcoin-purchase</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了价值近 16 亿美元的比特币，这是该公司自 1 月份以来最大的一次购买，该公司更加依赖于一种证券，该证券向投资者承诺，由同一加密货币支持的年度支付率为 11.5%。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ia_d3C2k3snA/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 14:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/saylor-s-strategy-ramps-up-sales-of-preferred-in-latest-bitcoin-purchase</guid></item><item><title>加密货币经纪商 BlockFills 在抛售后申请破产</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/crypto-trading-firm-blockfills-files-for-chapter-11-in-delaware</link><description>总部位于芝加哥的加密货币经纪和交易平台 BlockFills 在经历了数月的市场动荡，给整个行业的公司带来压力后，已申请破产保护。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.C2p51ZhHtk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 07:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/crypto-trading-firm-blockfills-files-for-chapter-11-in-delaware</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“旧经济”资产抢尽风头，比特币陷入困境</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-btc-in-iran-limbo-as-old-economy-assets-steal-limelight</link><description>比特币今年大部分时间都在 60,000 美元至 75,000 美元之间徘徊，反复酝酿突破，但从未真正实现突破。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iu4OnECC9wX0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 04:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-btc-in-iran-limbo-as-old-economy-assets-steal-limelight</guid></item></channel></rss>